name: Java-for-beginners
tagline: this is code, that helps java beginners, to get a hold of java, step by step
body:
### Welcome to the awesome world of Java.

I am Manasa Priyamvada Mannava and this is my attempt to simplify the process of learning Java. This is specially written for the beginners and helps them understand the basic OOPS concepts with the help of illustration examples. Hope this helps!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
